OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FCloud and
OL,6,Fpatchy rain moving southwards tonight,
OL,7,Fwith many places staying dry with
OL,8,Fclear spells. A few blustery showers
OL,9,Facross northern Scotland, turning
OL,10,Fwintry at times in the Northern Isles.
OL,11,FCold in the north with a rural frost.
OL,12,
OL,13,CWednesday:FMost places dry with patchy
OL,14,Fcloud and sunny spells. A few showers
OL,15,Fbreaking out across Northern Ireland,
OL,16,FWales and southwest England.
OL,17,FTemperatures below average for the
OL,18,Ftime of year.
